sentence.string: Last August five girls and two boys decided to go out bike riding in a thick heat wave.
We did not want to stay home and melt - so we rode on bike from Conshohocken to Philadelphia.
There was a bike route and we rode in line.

sentence.string: We got to a place - Row House Boat - for some cold drinks and a break.
We except one girl decided to continue with bike riding into downtown.
We did not pay any attention to time and realized it was late.
So we rode back to Row House Boat.
It was getting dark so we stopped at several places where they had phone booths to contact one of my roomate.
It was after nine pm - Not one of us had flash light or any light to guide us all back home.
We girls chickened out riding on bike route.
So we decided to give it a try to find our way back.
We made it worse and got lost.
I called in sick and told them that I fell off a bike and broke my thumb.
I went to doctor - got a note. and I went to an old drugstore to by a splinter.
So I will n^t get into trouble for calling in sick.
I ended up listening to all co workers making fun of me and my falling off bike!
